<DATE>
<P>
July 27, 1994, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 10; Column 4; National Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
820 words 
