<P>
Sidebar 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA072794-0128 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 064398 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
July 27, 1994, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 1; Column 4; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
