<HEADLINE>
<P>
BRIEFCASE: RETAIL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
Compiled by Greg Johnson / Times staff writer 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Farmers Market: The Lab, an eclectic blend of retail shops clustered in an old 
manufacturing building on Bristol Avenue in Costa Mesa, is now hosting a 
farmers market on Tuesdays. 
</P>
<P>
 The market's hours will 4 p.m. to 8 p.m. 
</P>
