<P>
 NYSE Chairman to Step Down: William H. Donaldson announced that he will not 
seek a new term at the New York Stock Exchange. Donaldson, 63, co-founder of 
Donaldson Lufkin & Jenrette, was reportedly under pressure from some members of 
