<TEXT>
<P>
 Wrong crossing -- A photograph published Monday depicted the wrong railroad 
crossing as the site of two fatal accidents in Moorpark. The photograph should 
have shown the crossing at California 118 west of Grimes Canyon Road. 
</P>
