<TEXT>
<P>
 Wrong information -- An article Tuesday misstated the average cost of 
development fees in Ventura County. The fees add $20,000 to $30,000 to the 
price of a single-family home, according to Dee Zinke, executive director of 
the regional Building Industry Assn. 
</P>
